article.title: ATK Awarded $86 Million Contract to Produce LW30mm M789 HEDP
article.author: Katie Packard
article.text: Alliant Techsystems has been awarded an $86 million contract to provide lightweight (LW) 30mm M789 High Explosive Dual Purpose (HEDP) tactical ammunition for the AH-64D Apache attack helicopter from the U.S. Army Contracting Command, Rock Island Contracting Center, Rock Island, Illinois.
